image_analysis.description: A photograph of an interior room viewed through a doorway. The room features a blue and white aesthetic with floral wallpaper, a large framed painting on the wall, and a dark blue reflective table. On the table sit two blue lamps. The floor has a white carpet with a blue grid pattern. A decorative vase sits on a pedestal in the background. The doorway frame is visible on the right side of the image.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot framed by a doorway on the right.
